Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　我らこそが災い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.64,utaware def,,0,0,0,,That is correct. Together, we are misfortune.
